reviewText: Follow up to Angel and Avenging Angel.  Tried to stretch the series too far.  Too many of the main characters from the first two movies were dead.  Couldn't maintain interest.
Movie is entertaining.  The story line is great, and the acting is great.
The entire Angel series is great to watch and tells a great story but does have sexual situations and some nudity.
All the Angel videos have different women playing "Angel". Of all of them, I think Mitzi is the best "Angel"! Glad I got it, you'll like it to, especially with all that 80's hair.
